# Ignore .claude/ contents (settings.local.json, transient lockfiles, etc.)
# but keep the skills/ subtree tracked so collaborators get them on clone.
# Note: ignore contents-of, not the directory itself — git won't descend
# into an ignored directory to evaluate negations.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
posthog-setup-report.md
